            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">Rachis </persName><rs
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldeus</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/2000">Vicalbo</placeName>
                        donavit <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84" key="#Monasteries">Beato
                            Benedicto</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> suam cum <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia Sancti
                            Victorini</rs> prope predictos <rs key="#Lakes">lacus, ubi modo Posta
                            vocatur</rs>, necnon et duo <rs key="#Gualdi">vvalda</rs><rs
                            key="#Gualdi #Fines"> in finibus Vicalbi</rs>, unum in <rs
                            key="#Forests #Other_administrative_unit">loco qui dicitur Silva
                            Plana</rs>, alterum in <rs key="#Mountains">monte Albeto</rs>, cum
                        omnibus <rs key="#Confinia">finibus ac pertinentiis</rs> ipsorum.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>Bloch 1986: 203, 820, 1348.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p><foreign>Ratchis</foreign>, gastaldo di Vicalvi, dona a Montecassino una
                        <foreign>curtis</foreign> con una chiesa di S. Vittorino vicino ai laghi
                        <foreign>Taurini et Iuliani</foreign>, nonché due gualdi nel territorio di
                    Vicalvi. Vedi il n. 321 del RPD e CMC, II, 6.</p>
            </div>
